MBALI KHANYILE KUTHOLAKALE imoto kaMnuz Nkosi Langa (33) wasePinetown osekuphele inyanga  amasonto amane  enyamalele, ngamaphoyisa kepha isishintshwe izinombolo zayo. Kuthiwa imoto itholakale ipakiwe ngo-Okthoba 23 eDalton, ngaseMgungundlovu ngenkathi amaphoyisa ephenya nge-Isizu D-Max 250 ebisolisa. solisayo. Ngokusho komthombo weSolezwe bathole ikhophi kamazisi, isifonyo nerisidi ye-airtime. Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uColonel Thembeka Mbele, uthe bathole imoto itholakele imotokodwa umnikazi akakatholakali. ubengakatholakali. “Imoto itholakale ipake eDalton, ikhiyiwe. Amaphoyisa ayaqhubeka nophenyo,” kusho uCol Mbele. UNksz Zodwa Langa udadewabo kaMnuz Langa, uthe sebehambe baze bafika emakhazeni befuna umfowabo kepha abamtholi. “Sicela othenge imoto asazise ukuthi ungakuphi umnikazi wayo, njengoba isitholakale isinenombolo entsha. Okubalulekile njengamanje wukutholakala komfowethu. Nabangani bayasiza, bazama ngokusemandleni ukusilekelela njengomndeni. Bukhulu kakhulu  ubuhlungu esikubo kumanje,” kubalisa uNksz Langa. ULanga owanyamalala ngoSepthemba 29 ebusuku kuthiwa waya endlini yakhe ese-Ashley, ePinetown, ewumuntu obuyayo. Kuthiwa ucingo lwakhe ahamba nalo lwagcina lungasangeni uma abomndeni bezama ukumfonela, nokuyilapho abasola ukuthi kukhona inkinga, baya emaphoyiseni beyobika ngokulahleka kwakhe. UMNUZ Nkosi Langa osathungathwa nokutholakale imoto yakhe eDalton ngaseMgungundlovu Isithombe: SITHUNYELWE